論文名稱(中文)
高爾夫開球桿之魅力研究


論文名稱(英文)
A Study on the Attractiveness of Golf Drivers


校院名稱
樹德科技大學


系所名稱(中)
應用設計研究所


系所名稱(英)
Graduate School of Applied Arts and Design


學年度
99


學期
2


出版年
100


研究生(中文)
鄭淑瑛


研究生(英文)
Chang, Shu-Ying


學位類別
碩士


語文別
中文


口試日期
2011-06-14


論文頁數
115頁


口試委員
指導教授-劉念德委員-吳昌祚委員-林群超


中文關鍵字

高爾夫開球桿；魅力工學；評價構造法        
                
              


英文關鍵字

Golf driver；Attractiveness engineering；Evaluation Grid Method (E.G.M.)        
                  
                


學科別分類



中文摘要

                     在世界運動的潮流以及國際上眾多明星球員的引領之下，近年來高爾夫運動越來越普遍成為全球性喜愛從事的運動項目之一，在已開發或開發中國家高爾夫球運動人口更是迅速地蓬勃發展，球桿需求因此逐年成長。   高爾夫運動是透過人與大自然的交匯，形成另一種文化風尚，既有體育運動的挑戰性及競技性，又富有娛樂、休閒、健身的內涵。在眾多體育運動中，高爾夫是全世界最不拘性別，適宜老、中、青、少各年齡層所從事有益身心健康的戶外綠地運動，因此有其特殊的魅力要素。   基於上述，本研究以高爾夫開球桿為題材，依據魅力工學的評價構造法(EvaluationGridMethod，簡稱E.G.M)，透過訪談10位愛好高爾夫運動的高涉入族群，捕捉對其物件的喜惡，並篩選萃取出4個原始魅力因子、22個具體魅力因子與10個抽象魅力因子。依循魅力工學訪談模式發展出10款構想設計案，並且進一步評估可行性以確立該項產品是否具有開發價值，以提供有效的產品設計定位。   研究發現高爾夫開球桿風格特質方面深受喜愛原因為「運動風格」、「休閒風格」、「尊貴典雅」、「科技風」等。而愛好高爾夫運動之球友對於高爾夫開球桿之產品設計平均認同程度皆為正向，因此透過本研究方法建立，可作為後續相關研究參考依據。
                


英文摘要

                     Recently golf is one of the favorite sports under the leadership of the movement trend by international golf stars. Golf players are rapidly increasing in the developed and developing countries. Therefore the clubs increased demand.   Golf has been forming unique cultural habit through the exchange of man and nature. It has been challenging sport, competitive, entertainment, leisure, fitness and cultural connotations. In many sports, golf is engaged in outdoor sports in the least by age and gender restrictions, so has its special attractiveness force elements.   In this study, the theme of golf drivers to explore the attractiveness factor of players. To estimate the preferences of the objects for 10 visitor with Evaluation Grid Method, it select four original attractiveness factor, twenty-two specific attractiveness factor and ten abstract factor as design project development basis. According to the survey conducted experimental data analysis to clarify the impact of consumer product design for golf driver satisfaction with the attractiveness of the important factors to provide effective product design.   The study demonstrated that the style of golf driver in the favorite character because as a "sporty", "casual style", "noble and elegant", "technology wind" and so on. The love of golf for golfers that the products design is all positive for the golf driver recognition. By establishing the research methods can be used as reference of the follow-up research.Keywords : Golf driver、Attractiveness engineering、Evaluation Grid Method(E.G.M.)
                


